Explaining business opportunities in the region during the inauguration of Business Forum organized by Tanzania Standard Newspapers Limited (TSN), RC Telack said Shinyanga has 240 industries, where213of them are medium scale. TSN is the publishers of Daily News, Sunday News, HabariLeo, HabariLeoJumapili and SpotiLeo newspapers. Meanwhile, Information,Culture, Arts and Sports Minister Dr Harrison Mwakyembe has said TSN’s Business Forum initiative is supporting the government’s effort of empowering youths economically. During the occasion, TSN Managing Editor Dr Jim Yonaz has said the Business Forum main focus is to ensure that the public become the major beneficiaries of all economic opportunities available in the country.